videos.headline: Joshua Jacobs flies down sidelines for big run
videos.description: Alabama RB Joshua Jacobs runs to the right side and breaks free down the sidelines for a 56-yard run.

videos.headline: Damien Harris breaks 57-yard run
videos.description: Damien Harris breaks 57-yard run

videos.headline: Hurts takes it in for 5-yard TD run
videos.description: Jalen Hurts runs it in from five yards out to give Alabama a 7-0 lead over Arkansas.

videos.headline: Alabama recovers Arkansas fumble on kickoff
videos.description: Adam Griffith kickoff for 64 yds , Deon Stewart return for 28 yds to the Ark 29 Deon Stewart fumbled, forced by Hootie Jones, recovered by Alab Mack Wilson

videos.headline: Dre Greenlaw carted off the field
videos.description: Arkansas LB was taken off the field on a cart after a right leg injury

videos.headline: Joshua Jacobs fumbles ball at goal line, Arkansas recovers
videos.description: Alabama RB Joshua Jacobs takes the handoff at the 1-yard line and is called down by contact. However, Arkansas asks the referee for a review. The refs take a look and determines that Jacobs lost the ball before going down and the Razorbacks recover.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Joshua Jacobs fumbles ball at goal line, Arkansas recovers) 2016/10/08

videos.headline: Hurts scores second rushing touchdown of game
videos.description: Alabama QB Jalen Hurts scores his second rushing touchdown, this time taking it in from six yards out to give the Crimson Tide a  14-0 lead over Arkansas.

videos.headline: Razorbacks strike for 24-yard TD
videos.description: Arkansas QB Austin Allen hits Jeremy Sprinkle for a 24-yard touchdown to cut Alabama's lead to 14-7.

videos.headline: Alabama returns fumble for touchdown
videos.description: Austin Allen run for no gain Austin Allen fumbled, forced by Da'Shawn Hand, recovered by Alab Tim Williams  , return for 23 yds

videos.headline: Allen fumble scooped up by Alabama for TD
videos.description: Alabama defensive lineman Da'Shawn Hand forces an Austin Allen fumble and Tim Williams returns it for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Allen fumble scooped up by Alabama for TD) 2016/10/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harris takes screen pass 56 yards for TD
videos.description: Alabama RB Damien Harris takes the screen pass and goes 56 yards, breaking tackles along the way, to put the Crimson Tide up 28-7 over Arkansas.

videos.headline: Bielema livid with officials after TD taken off board
videos.description: Bret Bielema takes his frustrations out on the officials after a holding penalty negated an Arkansas touchdown.

videos.headline: Scarbrough bursts to the outside on 21-yard TD
videos.description: Bo Scarbrough scores from 21 yards out to give Alabama a 35-10 lead over Arkansas.

videos.headline: Tide rolls past Arkansas 49-30
videos.description: Jalen Hurts throws four touchdowns and Minkah Fitzpatrick makes three interceptions as No. 1 Alabama extends its winning streak to 18 games with a 49-30 win over No. 16 Arkansas.
